HEADWORD: Canderos
<hw>Can"de*ros</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An East Indian
resin, of a pellucid white color, from which small ornaments and toys
are sometimes made.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Candescence</ent>⟦br⟧
